The strangest heroes we know are back for Season 3, but after Covid affected the Season 2 finale, would Doom Patrol be able to not only stick the landing but tread new ground for its 3rd Season? The answer to that question seems up for interpretation, as this season proves to be an abstract masterpiece aka glorious to some and messy to others. Join us as we gaze at the work of art that is Doom Patrol Season 3 and argue its merits as well as its downfalls. What do you got to lose? It's all Piffle Paffle anyway.   Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

